## PoiTableEntryDef interface

Interface for the JSON description of the \[\[PoiTableEntry\]\]. The interface is being implemented as \[\[PoiTableEntry\]\].

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface PoiTableEntryDef 
```
